**Alistair Delarusso's Reaction**: Doesn't hear the album directly — but hears ABOUT it. West End kids are talking about a new SD Media project featuring someone from America. Alistair's response is institutional contempt: "They're importing their dysfunction now. Lovely." He brings it up at a Prefect meeting as evidence that the Plaza situation is escalating. Recommends increasing Prefect patrols. What Alistair DOESN'T know is that Rax — sitting in the same meeting in his navy blazer — has the album on his phone and has already memorized Track 05.

